# Git workflow (NuRI)

- For non-trivial or multi-file changes, **work on a new branch** (`feat/…`, `fix/…`, `chore/…`), then **merge into `main`** (merge commit or PR), and push `main`.
- **Commit** reasonable progress when changes do **not** embed serious personal data (실명·연락처·API 시크릿·클라이언트 비밀키·로그인 토큰 등). Never commit `.env` (only `.env.example` without secrets).
- Do not commit junk lockfiles at repo root without a matching `package.json`.
